  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p618688/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201406/fe8260f5e08144458250099509603000.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tScientists at Harvard have confirmed a 19th century book in one of the university's libraries is bound in human skin.哈佛大学科学家已经证实，该校图书馆一本19世纪图书的封面材料取自人类皮肤。</p>\n<p>\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/conservator\" target=\"_blank\">Conservators</a> at the university carried out a series of tests on the binding, which left them '99.9% confident' the binding came from a human.哈弗大学管理员对该书封面做了一系列测试，称他们有&ldquo;99.9%的自信&rdquo; 肯定这本书的封面材料取自人类皮肤。</p>\n<p>\n\tThe book, Ars&egrave;ne Houssaye's Des destin&eacute;es de l'ame, which translates as The Destiny Of The Soul, is described as a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/meditation\" target=\"_blank\">meditation</a> on the soul and life after death and is believed to have been bound in skin from the unclaimed body of a female mental patient.本书原名<em>Ars&egrave;ne Houssaye's Des destin&eacute;es de l'ame</em> ，翻译过来就是《灵魂的归宿》。据说这本书的主要内容是对死亡后灵魂和生命的沉思，其封面材料取自一个女精神病人的皮肤。</p>\n<p>\n\tScientists confirmed the binding on the book, housed in the Houghton Library, is human skin after using a technique known as <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/peptide\" target=\"_blank\">peptide</a> mass fingerprintings to analyse <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/microscopic\" target=\"_blank\">microscopic</a> samples.这本书陈列在哈佛大学霍顿图书馆。科学家使用&ldquo;肽质量指纹图谱&rdquo;技术分析显微样品后，确认该书封面由人皮制成。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201406/7b7486fb409f4f1d8a561069401dd807.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tIn a blogpost on the library's website, Heather Cole, Assistant Curator of Modern Books & <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/manuscript\" target=\"_blank\">Manuscripts</a>, claims Bouland bound the book with skin from the unclaimed body of a female mental patient who died of a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stroke\" target=\"_blank\">stroke</a>.希瑟&middot;科尔是&ldquo;当代图书&rdquo;分馆的助理馆长。他在图书馆网站上的一篇文章中说道，卢多维奇用一位死于中风的女精神病人的皮肤制成了该书封面。</p>\n<p>\n\tHoussaye is believed to have presented the book to his friend Dr Ludovic Bouland.据称当年是希瑟把这本书呈递给他的朋友卢多维奇博士进行封装的。</p>\n<p>\n\tA note inside the book, written by Ludovic, reads: 'A book about the human soul deserved to have a human covering: I had kept this piece of human skin taken from the back of a woman.'书中留下了一张卢多维奇写的字条：&ldquo;一本有关人类灵魂的书，值得用人类皮肤来封装：本书封皮是我用一个女人背部的皮肤制成的。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\tIn the note, Ludovic also refers to another book bound in human skin, S&eacute;verin Pineau&rsquo;s De integritatis & corruptionis virginum notis, which is in the Wellcome Library collection.在字条中，卢多维奇还提到了另外一本人皮书&mdash;&mdash;现存于英国伦敦维尔康姆图书馆中的<em>S&eacute;verin Pineau&rsquo;s De integritatis & corruptionis virginum notis</em>。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p618688/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p618688\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p488758/\">强化直达：两个月突破四六级新题型！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p617207/\">10分钟就能学会的25条生活小贴士（上）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p617151/\">发型影响年龄：中分老7岁 右分年轻5岁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p618433/\">全民动员 形形色色看千万高考大军</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p618428/\">日本为强制“加班族”休假而创建全国性假日</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p617869/\">世界上适合单独旅行的9大目的地</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p611104/\">国际商务英语：情景沟通中的学习</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p614061/\">2014年6月英语四级作文预测：假期综合症</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p614040/\">2014年6月英语六级作文预测：能力与外貌</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
